Client (Frontend - Week 5)          Backend API (This Week)
┌──────────────────────┐            ┌────────────────────────┐
│ Select file (2GB WSI)│            │  POST /upload-start    │
│ Split into chunks    │────────┐   │  Create temp session   │
│ (5MB each)           │        └──▶│  Return sessionId      │
│ Send chunk 1, 2, 3.. │            │                        │
└──────────────────────┘   ┌────────▶│  POST /upload-chunk    │
     User sees:            │        │  Verify chunk #        │
     [====  40% done]      │        │  Save to disk/S3       │
                           │        │  Return next chunk #   │
                           │        │                        │
                           └────────▶│  POST /upload-complete │
                                     │  Merge chunks          │
                                     │  Validate file         │
                                     │  Store metadata in DB  │
                                     │  Return fileId         │
                                     └────────────────────────┘
